    "It was considered important to know how the user felt during the experience, in the areas which assessed emotions: such as Psychology, Medicine, and Education and Training.",
    "The second most evaluated topic was Experience features (19.9%).",
    "In that category, user opinions were evaluated on the characteristics of the experience (i.e., cybersickness, and sense of embodiment).",
    "Its assessment was through surveys and interviews.",
    "In addition, it was used in most fields, with the exception of Tourism and Marketing."
